                <h4>Setting up Payment Information - Onboarding & My Waffle House</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>UIS technical doesn't assist with banking information set up in the onboarding process or on my.wafflehouse.com. </li>
                    <li>The payment information section of the onboarding process can be skipped by filling out a "Stand Alone I9." The "Stand alone I9" can be found on the onboarding screen. It's the last option. </li>
                    <li>OSS/Area Admin assists with banking information set up if an associate is having trouble entering the information in on my.wafflehouse.com. A manager and associate need to be present for OSS to assist with banking information setup. </li>
