            <div class="panel-body">
                <h4>Grill Operators raising hand</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>The associate should go to career advancement and select the <b>Master Grill Operator</b> button if they are a grill operator or select  <b>Rockstar Grill Operator</b> if they are a master grill operator</li>
                    <li>Only Master Grill Operators can select Rockstar Grill Operator.  Regular associates cannot.</li>
                    <li>Once the associate has selected either option. they should hit <b>apply</b>.  A Certify notification will be sent to the division manager's ops express elvis admin list of grill ops waiting to be promoted. </li>
                    <li> The division manager must certify a grill op's promotion to Master or Rockstar.</li>
                </ul>

